#: ../../docs/gentle_gis_introduction/authors_and_contributors.rst:4
msgid "About the authors & contributors"
msgstr "O autorima i saradnicima"

#: ../../docs/gentle_gis_introduction/authors_and_contributors.rst:15
msgid ""
"Tim Sutton --- Editor & Lead Author. Tim is a developer and project steering"
" committee member of the QGIS project. He is passionate about seeing GIS "
"being Freely available to everyone. Tim is also a founding member of "
"Linfiniti Consulting CC. --- a small business set up with the goal of "
"helping people to learn and use opensource GIS software. **Web**: "
"https://kartoza.com **Email**: tim@kartoza.com"
msgstr ""
"Tim Saton --- Urednik i glavni autor. Tim je programer i član upravnog "
"odbora projekta QGIS. Strastveno se zalaže za to da GIS bude besplatno "
"dostupan svima. Tim je takođe jedan od osnivača Linfiniti Consulting CC. ---"
" malog preduzeća osnovanog sa ciljem da pomogne ljudima da uče i koriste "
"GIS softver otvorenog koda. **Veb**: https://kartoza.com **E-pošta**: "
"tim@kartoza.com"

#: ../../docs/gentle_gis_introduction/authors_and_contributors.rst:26
msgid ""
"Otto Dassau --- Assistant Author. Otto Dassau is the documentation "
"maintainer and project steering committee member of the QGIS project. Otto "
"has considerable experience in using and training people to use Free and "
"Open Source GIS software. **Web**: http://www.nature-consult.de **Email**: "
"otto.dassau@gmx.de"
msgstr ""
"Oto Dasau --- Pomoćnik autora. Oto Dasau je održavalac dokumentacije i član"
" upravnog odbora projekta QGIS. Oto ima značajno iskustvo u korišćenju i "
"obuci ljudi za korišćenje besplatnog i otvorenog GIS softvera. **Veb**: "
"http://www.nature-consult.de **E-pošta**: otto.dassau@gmx.de"

#: ../../docs/gentle_gis_introduction/authors_and_contributors.rst:36
msgid ""
"Marcelle Sutton --- Project Manager. Marcelle Sutton studied English and "
"drama and is a qualified teacher. Marcelle is also a founding member of "
"Linfiniti Consulting CC. --- a small business set up with the goal of "
"helping people to learn and use opensource GIS software. **Web**: "
"https://kartoza.com **Email**: marcelle@kartoza.com"
msgstr ""
"Marsel Saton --- Rukovodilac projekta. Marsel Saton je studirala engleski "
"jezik i dramu i kvalifikovani je nastavnik. Marsel je takođe jedan od "
"osnivača Linfiniti Consulting CC. --- malog preduzeća osnovanog sa ciljem "
"da pomogne ljudima da uče i koriste GIS softver otvorenog koda. **Veb**: "
"https://kartoza.com **E-pošta**: marcelle@kartoza.com"

#: ../../docs/gentle_gis_introduction/authors_and_contributors.rst:44
msgid ""
"Lerato Nsibande --- Video Presenter. Lerato is a grade 12 scholar living in "
"Pretoria. Lerato learns Geography at school and has enjoyed learning GIS "
"with us!"
msgstr ""
"Lerato Nsibande --- Video prezenter. Lerato je učenik 12. razreda koji živi "
"u Pretoriji. Lerato uči geografiju u školi i uživao je učeći GIS sa nama!"

#: ../../docs/gentle_gis_introduction/authors_and_contributors.rst:51
msgid ""
"Sibongile Mthombeni --- Video Presenter. Sibongile lives near Johannesburg "
"with her young daughter. Her goal is to continue her studies and become a "
"nurse. Working on this project was the first time Sibongile used a computer."
msgstr ""
"Sibongile Mtombeni --- Video prezenter. Sibongile živi blizu Johanesburga sa"
" svojom malom ćerkom. Njen cilj je da nastavi studije i postane medicinska "
"sestra. Rad na ovom projektu je bio prvi put da je Sibongile koristila "
"računar."
